# Pickup
This is a simple mod which allows us to pick up item directly from the item frame.
# New interacting logic
Hand:Empty + Item Frame:Stored -> Pick up item;  
Hand:Stored + Item Frame:Empty -> Store item;  
Hand:Stored + Item Frame:Stored + Sneaking -> Exchange item;  
Others -> Rotate item.  
# Note
如果你是中文用户，你可以选择访问[MCMOD](https://www.mcmod.cn/class/13617.html)。
